# Composer conventions

- PHP `^8.3`, PHPUnit `^10.5`. `minimum-stability: dev`, `prefer-stable: true`.
- Sibling deps: `"sugarcraft/<dep>": "@dev"` in `require` AND path-repo in `repositories` (`{type: path, url: "../<dep>", options: {symlink: true}}`).
- Path-repos must cover the FULL transitive closure — copy from `sugar-charts/composer.json` and prune unused.
- Metadata block (after `license`, before `require`): `keywords` (lowercase kebab, include `"sugarcraft"` + upstream Go name), `homepage: "https://github.com/sugarcraft/<slug>"`, single author `Joe Huss <detain@interserver.net>` role `Maintainer`, `support.{issues,source,docs}`.
- PSR-4: `"<NS>\\<Sub>\\": "src/"` + matching test namespace. Quirk: `candy-core` → `SugarCraft\\Core\\`.
- `composer validate --strict` flags every `"@dev"` — EXPECTED, drop `--strict`.
- New lib also touches: root `composer.json`, `.github/workflows/ci.yml` matrix, `.github/workflows/vhs.yml` matrix, `README.md`, `MATCHUPS.md`, `docs/index.html`, `docs/lib/<slug>.html`, `media/icons/<slug>.png`, `codecov.yml`.
